The '''Series IV picket ship''' was a type of small [[Warship/Legends|warship]] which was developed and manufactured by [[Cindev]]. The [[Buzzzer (starship)|''Buzzzer'']], a known [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] vessel operating in the [[Corellian system/Legends|Corellian system]], was one such ship of this class.

